  "text": "In order to avoid such a phenomenon, it is required to reduce the stochastic noise on the DSMC solution, and this can be done using suitable time space averages (see for instance, [CITATION_1] ), smoothing the solution as in [CITATION_2] or increasing the number of particles used to compute the DSMC solution. In all cases the computational cost of the simulation increases.",
